ARIES MAN
Aries men can choose woody, floral notes of musk: musk, violet, freesia, patchouli, amber, geranium, mint, pine, rosemary and jasmine scents.
 Men by Marc Jacobs
 Egoiste Platinum for men by Chanel
Touch for men by Burberry

ARIES WOMAN
The courageous and dynamic Aries woman, whose energy is endless, attracts all eyes with her adventurous spirit. Very mild fragrances are not much for Aries, they like the claim. For this reason, woody and floral scents are ideal for Aries women.
Dolce&Gabbana The One
Yves Rocher Evidence Intense
Marc Jacobs Daisy Dream
